Happy New Year 2023!!!
I wish you all joy and positive mindset on whatever you’ll do! 
These pictures are my “feel” for this new year.
My year looks already very exciting with lots of touring, working on new music with @apocalypticaofficial and other projects, coaching, creating and launching new things etc… Even it seems very busy my main goal is to do everything joyfully, consciously and gratefully. Learn more about myself. To focus more on “how to be” than “how to do”, as “being” and acting from within leads into better action. 

“Take care of yourself, take care of each other, love each other and love yourself”

#newyear #positivethinking #lifecoaching #selfdevelopment #learntobe #apocalyptica #cello #touring #fullpotential

A little moment of peace and joy… 

Enjoying fantastic late breakfast in Lima with the best ever pineapple juice!!! 
This tour has been pretty insane with intense travel and lack of sleep but filled with the energy from incredible people at the shows!!! 

No matter how busy the life is, it is important to create little moments of peace for ourselves, every day. Sit down, take a breather and observe how we feel, look around how beautiful life is and appreciate the fact that we are alive…

I’m so excited for the show tonight!!! First Apocalyptica show in Peru!!!

Last weekend was my very first time to experience the @f1 and it was mind blowing!!! The rain made the race so exciting even @maxverstappen1 won as expected 😅
i’ve been following F1 from tv already since the 80’s when #kekerosberg was driving. Hyvää Itsenäisyyspäivää Suomi!!
Happy Independence Day Finland!!! 🇫🇮

Here are few captures of Finland through my eyes. 

I am so grateful that I was born and grew up in this beautiful country of ”Thousand lakes”.
Small but strong and free country which the generation of my grandparents were fighting and dying for. 
Country of the weirdest and one of the most difficult languages existing, one of the best on free education, healthcare and general safety in the world. ”Quiet” but honest people who love ”social distance”. And pretty clean air and nature. What else can you wish for?

Kiitos!!! 

p.s. The accurate number of lakes is 168.000

Diving into 2024 with this attitude; awake, excited, curious, eager to learn, ready to execute and deliver!!! 

Happy New Year Everyone!!! 💥✨🔥🌟

2023 was a big year for me with so many great things happening…

Lots of personal work and growth. 

Great shows with Apocalyptica: Epic Apocalypse Tour with @epicaofficial and @resident.wheel , South-American Tour and the Church Tour “Journey Into The Mind” with the Live Album release. 
“What We’re Up Against”-single with @elizeryd. 
Recorded a new studio album which will be out 2024.

Beside the intense Apo-stuff I finished the @brightandblack_ album which will be out in January and on tour in March. 

Released my autobiography, @vaegardesign jewelry brand and worked with my coaching clients. Writing this all down feels it’s been a lot which is actually very true 😅😄 

Luckily I have learned to value rest and time with my loved ones so life has been mainly in a good balance, even time to time it has been exhausting and challenges have been huge sometimes. 

I know 2024 is not gonna be any less adventurous and I am ready!!! 

Thank you all for being part of my year!!! 
May the New Year bring good things to all of us 🙏🥰

#happynewyear #newyear #grateful
